T1  - The Multinational Corporation in the Less Developed Country: The Economic Development Model Versus the North-South Model
AU  - Paul, Karen
AU  - Barbato, Robert
Y1  - 1985/01/01
PY  - 1985
DA  - 1985/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1985.4277326
